
# BusinessInteractionManager Database (Windows Oracle XE)

## Project Overview

* **Name:** Turikumana Jean Claude
* **Student ID:** 26989

---

## Database Setup (Windows)

### **1. Create Pluggable Database (PDB)**

**Switch to root container:**

```sql
ALTER SESSION SET CONTAINER=CDB$ROOT;
```

**Create PDB:**

```sql
CREATE PLUGGABLE DATABASE Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB
ADMIN USER Claude_Admin IDENTIFIED BY Claude
FILE_NAME_CONVERT=(
  'C:/APP/BELLO/PRODUCT/21C/ORADATA/XE/PDBSEED/',
  'C:/APP/BELLO/PRODUCT/21C/ORADATA/XE/Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB/'
);
```

**Open the PDB:**

```sql
ALTER PLUGGABLE DATABASE Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB OPEN;
```

**Verify PDB:**

```sql
SHOW PDBS;
```

---

### **2. Create Tablespaces**

**Switch to your PDB:**

```sql
ALTER SESSION SET CONTAINER=Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB;
```

**Data Tablespace:**

```sql
CREATE TABLESPACE Mon_26989_Data
DATAFILE 'C:/APP/BELLO/PRODUCT/21C/ORADATA/XE/Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB/Mon_26989_Data01.dbf'
SIZE 100M AUTOEXTEND ON NEXT 10M MAXSIZE UNLIMITED;
```

**Index Tablespace:**

```sql
CREATE TABLESPACE Mon_26989_Index
DATAFILE 'C:/APP/BELLO/PRODUCT/21C/ORADATA/XE/Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB/Mon_26989_Index01.dbf'
SIZE 50M AUTOEXTEND ON NEXT 10M MAXSIZE UNLIMITED;
```

**Temporary Tablespace:**

```sql
CREATE TEMPORARY TABLESPACE Mon_26989_Temp
TEMPFILE 'C:/APP/BELLO/PRODUCT/21C/ORADATA/XE/Mon_26989_Claude_BusinessInteractionManager_DB/Mon_26989_Temp01.dbf'
SIZE 50M AUTOEXTEND ON NEXT 10M MAXSIZE UNLIMITED;
```

---

### **3. User Setup**

**Create Admin User:**

```sql
CREATE USER Claude_Admin IDENTIFIED BY Claude
DEFAULT TABLESPACE Mon_26989_Data
TEMPORARY TABLESPACE Mon_26989_Temp;

GRANT CONNECT, RESOURCE, DBA TO Claude_Admin;
```

**Verify User:**

```sql
SELECT username, default_tablespace, temporary_tablespace
FROM dba_users
WHERE username='CLAUDE_ADMIN';
```

---

### **4. Memory Settings (Windows)**

**Set SGA and PGA:**

```sql
ALTER SYSTEM SET sga_target = 500M SCOPE=BOTH;
ALTER SYSTEM SET pga_aggregate_target = 200M SCOPE=BOTH;
```

**Verify Memory:**

```sql
SHOW PARAMETER sga_target;
SHOW PARAMETER pga_aggregate_target;
```

---

### **5. Enable and Verify ARCHIVELOG Mode (Windows)**

**Switch to CDB root and mount database:**

```sql
ALTER SESSION SET CONTAINER=CDB$ROOT;
SHUTDOWN IMMEDIATE;
STARTUP MOUNT;
ALTER DATABASE ARCHIVELOG;
ALTER DATABASE OPEN;
ALTER PLUGGABLE DATABASE ALL OPEN;
```

**Verify Archive Log:**

```sql
ARCHIVE LOG LIST;
```

Expected Output:

Database log mode              Archive Mode
Automatic archival             Enabled
Archive destination            C:\APP\BELLO\PRODUCT\21C\HOMES\OraDB21Home1\RDBMS
Oldest online log sequence     55
Current log sequence           57

